               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph/>
                  <paragraph>Proparacaine hydrochloride ophthalmic solution 0.5% is supplied 
in 15 mL DROP-TAINER® dispensers.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">NDC </content># 16590-195-15<br/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
